{"id": "art-448", "label": "Art. 448", "title": "Art. 448: Soluţiile la judecata recursului în casaţie", "slug": "art-448", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1805760429\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1539\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1805760429\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 448:\nSolu&#355;iile la judecata recursului în casa&#355;ie </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_339746712\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1538\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_339746712\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Instan&#355;a,\njudecând recursul în casa&#355;ie, pronun&#355;&#259; una dintre\nurm&#259;toarele solu&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1331114218\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1537\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1331114218\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>1.respinge recursul în casa&#355;ie, men&#355;inând\nhot&#259;rârea atacat&#259;, dac&#259; recursul în casa&#355;ie este nefondat;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_886168669\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1536\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_886168669\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>2.<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>admite recursul în\ncasa&#355;ie, casând hot&#259;rârea atacat&#259;, &#351;i:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1646849911\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1535\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1646849911\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)îl achit&#259; pe inculpat sau dispune încetarea\nprocesului penal ori înl&#259;tur&#259; gre&#351;ita aplicare a legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1265851678\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1534\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1265851678\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)dispune rejudecarea de c&#259;tre instan&#355;a de apel\nori de c&#259;tre instan&#355;a competent&#259; material sau dup&#259;\ncalitatea persoanei, dac&#259; sunt incidente celelalte cazuri de casare prev&#259;zute\nla art. 438.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_490563021\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1533\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_490563021\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; recursul în casa&#355;ie vizeaz&#259;\ngre&#351;ita solu&#355;ionare a laturii civile, instan&#355;a, dup&#259;\nadmiterea recursului, înl&#259;tur&#259; nelegalitatea constatat&#259; sau\ndispune rejudecarea de c&#259;tre instan&#355;a a c&#259;rei hot&#259;râre a\nfost casat&#259;, în condi&#355;iile alin. (1) pct. 2 lit. b).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2098926523\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1532\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2098926523\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1) pct. 2 lit. a)\ninstan&#355;a de recurs în casa&#355;ie desfiin&#355;eaz&#259; &#351;i\nhot&#259;rârea primei instan&#355;e, dac&#259; se constat&#259; acelea&#351;i\nînc&#259;lc&#259;ri de lege ca în decizia recurat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1376747466\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1531\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1376747466\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul în care condamnatul se g&#259;se&#351;te în\ncursul execut&#259;rii pedepsei, instan&#355;a, admi&#355;ând recursul în\ncasa&#355;ie &#351;i pronun&#355;ând casarea cu trimitere, dispune asupra\nst&#259;rii de libertate a acestuia, putând lua o m&#259;sur&#259;\npreventiv&#259;.</span></p>"}